{"tid":842110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來飼養兔仔可令人心境平靜！🌟","createTime":"2018-09-30T04:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T15:15:20.000Z","uid":197098,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bc54d9e6dc9e3a21a001b31f214f91e3da2c43a4","tid":842110,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:58:17.000Z","msg":"兔子是其中一種最心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們尤其是咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是兔子的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響的。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<br />\n以下video可看到兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人！☺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=sEtQ1DUxG56JTG4DW6ZSvxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=8bc8422c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a><br />\n<br />\n當兔子跳兔子舞(Binky)時, 這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活，因為兔子Binky是兔子最開心的狀態。以下video可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=sEtQ1DUxG56JTG4DW6ZSvxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d051fe82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">N.B.: </span>實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>參觀然後領養</strong></span>，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=sEtQ1DUxG56JTG4DW6ZSvxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=2fa6dc9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"a9cd3f0179b77edd780500e164eb6e278dc3583e","tid":842110,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:58:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0j8Gt5JQPKc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0j8Gt5JQPKc&d=sEtQ1DUxG56JTG4DW6ZSvxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=754a06b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0j8Gt5JQPKc</a>"},{"pid":"8a45c426e05b7e7342ba62884c884a2fae8dc3bf","tid":842110,"uid":92680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"你使唔使開到嚟娛樂台呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8057b067fefcec40ccb62358957b7a4e17810647","tid":842110,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:15:20.000Z","msg":"......"}]}